site.name: designated site name
crew: full names separated by commas
min.searching: number of minutes spent searching for fish
so.total: total sockeye in net (rounded to nearest 10,100, or 1000)
cu.total: total chum in net (rounded to nearest 10,100, or 1000)
he.total: total herring in net (rounded to nearest 10,100, or 1000)
co.total: total coho in net (rounded to nearest 10,100, or 1000)
pi.total: total pink in net (rounded to nearest 10,100, or 1000)
bycatch.num.1:
number of bycatch species #1 in net
(NA if none)
bycatch.num.2:
number of bycatch species #2 in net
(NA if none)
bycatch.num.3:
number of bycatch species #3 in net
(NA if none)
mort.num.1:
number of mort species #1 in net
(NA if none)
mort.num.2:
number of mort species #2 in net
(NA if none)
mort.num.3:
number of mort species #3 in net
(NA if none)
preserved:
1 = preserved correctly
0 = not correctly
TBD = in dewar
